# Windsurf Rules - React Native Expo Template

Follow `AGENTS.md` and `CONVENTIONS.md`. When they conflict, prefer `CONVENTIONS.md` for code style and `AGENTS.md` for agent workflow.

## Stack

- React Native 0.83.2 + Expo SDK 55
- expo-router with typed routes
- TypeScript 5.9 strict
- react-native-unistyles 3.x
- @tanstack/react-query
- Zustand
- Supabase with graceful degradation
- Axios client in `@/services/api`
- react-i18next with English, Vietnamese, Simplified Chinese, and Traditional Chinese
- react-native-mmkv
- react-hook-form + zod/v4

## Must Follow

- Use `yarn` only.
- `yarn validate` runs `type-check`, `lint`, `format:check`, and `i18n:check`.
- Use `StyleSheet` from `react-native-unistyles`.
- Never use inline styles, color literals, or hardcoded spacing.
- Use project components from `@/common/components`.
- Translate every user-facing string with `useTranslation` and update all locale files (`en.json`, `vi.json`, `zh-CN.json`, `zh-TW.json`).
- Auth state lives only in `useAuthStore`.
- Server state goes through React Query; client state goes through Zustand selectors.
- API calls go through `@/services/api`.
- Forms use `react-hook-form` + `zod/v4`.
- No `any`, no suppression comments, no `--no-verify`.

## Repo Facts

- `app/` contains `(auth)` and `(main)` route groups.
- `app/_layout.tsx` wires gesture handling, error boundary, query provider, alert provider, bottom sheet provider, camera provider, auth init, and toast.
- `src/common/components/index.ts` is the public barrel for shared UI components.
- `src/theme/index.ts` exposes semantic theme tokens, and `src/theme/metrics.ts` exposes `rf`, `hs`, `vs`, `spacing`, `spacingV`, `fontSize`, `borderRadius`, and `iconSize`.
